humin
=====

converts seconds to human readable format. inspired by z3bra's human(1): http://git.z3bra.org/human/file/README.html.

installation
------------

	# build humin
	make
	# install (defaults to /usr/local/bin)
	make install
	
	# install to custom PREFIX (binary is installed at /home/me/bin)
	make PREFIX=/home/me install 

	# uninstall (add PREFIX option like above to uninstall from custom location)
	make uninstall
usage
-----

	# convert 300 seconds to 'hh:mm:ss'
	humin 300
	00:05:00

	# convert 87000 seconds to 'dd days hh:mm:ss'
	humin 87000
	01 days 00:10:00

